snippet.title: AllRedding.com | Episode 4: Interview with Dr. Cheryl Serr, Amber Health Care for Women
snippet.description:
In this 4th episode of AllRedding.com, we introduce you to Dr. Cheryl Serr, the owner of Amber Health Care for Women, and Chief of Surgery at Patients Hospital.

In this episode, your local All Redding host, Joey Gartin of WebDrvn, interviews Dr. Cheryl Serr, where they discuss various topics ranging from Women's Health, Autism, balancing being a Dr. and Mother, and an amazing story of courage and strength as she discusses her own mother, who was a strong intelligent woman who lived through the Cuban Revolution.
